page.title: 19HAVANT THICKET-DETAIL
page.content:
On our visit to Havant Thicket in June 1985 we identified the following: EVERGREEN TREES- Yew Corsican Pine Douglas Fir Western Hemlock Scots Pine Western Red Cedar Norway Spruce
DECIDUOUS TREES- Hornbeam Pedunculate Oak Red Oak Ash Aspen Beech Great Sallow Silver Birch Hazel Sweet Chestnut Sycamore
OTHER PLANTS/FLOWERS- Gorse Bracket Fungus Elder Holly Cinquefoil Lichen Moss Goose Grass Foxglove Ivy Buttercups Bluebells Common Spotted Orchids Bracken
by Rosemary Knight & Katherine Nalder
